WEBVTT

00:08:29.128 --> 00:08:31.461
and he was like, "No, no and no."

00:08:31.485 --> 00:08:32.636
And I got mad,

00:08:32.660 --> 00:08:36.597
like, how dare he not embrace
my brilliant wisdom?

00:08:36.621 --> 00:08:38.337
(Laughter)

00:08:38.361 --> 00:08:41.827
And then I remembered
times I've been depressed,

00:08:41.851 --> 00:08:46.467
and how I thought I was doomed
in all possible futures,

00:08:46.491 --> 00:08:50.163
or everybody suddenly hated me,
and things like that.

00:08:51.498 --> 00:08:54.717
It didn't matter how many people
told me otherwise --

00:08:54.741 --> 00:08:56.144
I didn't believe them.

00:08:57.220 --> 00:09:00.308
So I let my friend know I cared,